1
00:00:58,014 --> 00:01:00,990
=Within The Grip=

2
00:01:00,990 --> 00:01:02,960
=Episode 20=

3
00:01:02,960 --> 00:01:06,982
(Spark of Love)

4
00:01:10,400 --> 00:01:14,400
The newly deceased Gu Zhaoxi
looked remarkably like me.

5
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:15,359
Upon investigation,

6
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:20,439
he turned out to be my brother, Yin Ci,
whom we all believed died years ago.

7
00:01:21,439 --> 00:01:22,359
How could it be?

8
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:25,400
"Newly deceased?" He's already...?

9
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:31,439
Was the assassin
back then really Gu Jiang?

10
00:01:32,719 --> 00:01:35,079
What exactly happened?

11
00:01:36,159 --> 00:01:41,159
Gu Jiang, Yun Sui and your mother Lianyi

12
00:01:41,319 --> 00:01:42,480
were from the same sect.

13
00:01:43,439 --> 00:01:47,239
The Xuanji Pavilion was co-founded
by your mother and Yun Sui.

14
00:01:49,079 --> 00:01:51,680
But they both fell in love
with those they shouldn't have.

15
00:01:52,519 --> 00:01:53,959
Lianyi married into the palace.

16
00:01:54,239 --> 00:01:56,239
Your father held
no real power at that time,

17
00:01:57,159 --> 00:02:02,560
so she used the Xuanji Pavilion
to consolidate your father's position.

18
00:02:03,719 --> 00:02:05,159
But that didn't last long.

19
00:02:06,359 --> 00:02:10,680
To secure the throne, your father
married the Right Chancellor's daughter.

20
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:12,479
Later,

21
00:02:13,960 --> 00:02:16,000
on her way back
to the Tianji Sect to pay respects,

22
00:02:17,199 --> 00:02:19,080
Lianyi was ambushed.

23
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:28,159
Go!

24
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:29,719
My lady!

25
00:02:36,599 --> 00:02:37,199
Stop!

26
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:39,199
Don't run!

27
00:02:43,919 --> 00:02:44,520
Lianyi!

28
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:49,000
- I'm too late.
- Save Ci!

29
00:02:49,639 --> 00:02:52,240
Ye Lan and Ci are over there.
Go save him now!

30
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:52,860
Alright.

31
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,080
Lianyi!

32
00:03:01,919 --> 00:03:06,120
I arrived too late and could
only rescue you as an infant.

33
00:03:07,319 --> 00:03:11,439
I searched relentlessly
but never found your brother.

34
00:03:13,439 --> 00:03:15,680
I failed to protect your mother,

35
00:03:16,919 --> 00:03:18,800
and I betrayed her trust.

36
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:24,240
The Xuanji Pavilion only
answers to the Master's token.

37
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,960
Since Gu Jiang took over,

38
00:03:27,479 --> 00:03:30,879
it's been no longer what it once was.

39
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,520
Someone intended to assassinate you

40
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,439
in such a short time.

41
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:41,560
If the deceased one was truly Yin Ci,

42
00:03:42,319 --> 00:03:44,560
his death would certainly be suspicious.

43
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:50,240
That woman involved can't be innocent.

44
00:03:51,039 --> 00:03:52,000
Remember this.

45
00:03:52,639 --> 00:03:55,439
Don't let anyone in the Gu family
discover your identity.

46
00:04:00,919 --> 00:04:04,080
Our priority now isn't damage control.

47
00:04:04,719 --> 00:04:08,199
We must uncover the true mastermind
behind Gu Zhaoxi's murder.

48
00:04:09,319 --> 00:04:12,520
But our people kept watch day and night.

49
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:16,120
Before this Heaven task, nothing moved
in or out of the Gu Mansion.

50
00:04:17,439 --> 00:04:19,680
How exactly did they
receive task orders?

51
00:04:22,399 --> 00:04:25,079
What have you discovered
about the person I told you to watch?

52
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:27,600
No leads yet.

53
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:33,240
With today's clues,
you'll uncover something soon.

54
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:34,000
Go now.

55
00:04:34,639 --> 00:04:35,139
Yes.

56
00:04:39,136 --> 00:04:42,920
(Fufeng Pavilion)

57
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:44,000
(Looking back now,)

58
00:04:44,759 --> 00:04:46,800
(on the night
of Zuixian Building's owner's death,)

59
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:48,360
(Zhaoxi was nearby too.)

60
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:50,344
(Shen Zetian)

61
00:04:50,519 --> 00:04:51,839
(But I have a feeling.)

62
00:04:52,399 --> 00:04:54,600
(Someone has been guiding
me to investigate this.)

63
00:04:59,279 --> 00:05:02,040
(If these accidents were truly planned
by the Xuanji Pavilion...)

64
00:05:04,398 --> 00:05:07,181
(Heaven)

65
00:05:07,959 --> 00:05:11,279
(It seems I must infiltrate
the Pavilion again.)

66
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:23,920
(Xuanji Pavilion)

67
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:25,360
Why isn't Mr. Gu Xuanwu here today?

68
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:27,079
He's on a task.

69
00:05:27,199 --> 00:05:28,680
Still calling him that?

70
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:31,600
When he returns, we might need
to address him as Pavilion Master.

71
00:05:32,839 --> 00:05:33,639
Right.

72
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:27,319
- Dear?
- Honey?

73
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:33,240
Who would've thought my frail husband

74
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:34,839
possesses such skills?

75
00:06:35,839 --> 00:06:40,319
Shouldn't you be resting?
Why the night stroll in black clothes?

76
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,560
Likewise.

77
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:54,368
(Heaven)

78
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:58,360
Aren't you afraid I'll call
for help, acting so openly?

79
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:03,480
If you weren't afraid
of being discovered,

80
00:07:03,879 --> 00:07:06,040
you wouldn't be wearing this outfit.

81
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:10,199
Besides, I doubt you'd want me captured.

82
00:07:12,439 --> 00:07:14,839
That depends on who gets it first.

83
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:20,560
If I'm not mistaken,

84
00:07:20,879 --> 00:07:22,639
you were the one at the Xuanji Pavilion.

85
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:57,720
And also the one
who secretly aided Xuan Qing.

86
00:08:22,319 --> 00:08:23,759
Since you already know,

87
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:26,759
shall we work together from now on?

88
00:08:39,399 --> 00:08:41,039
Intruders in the Shadow Pavilion! Go!

89
00:08:41,279 --> 00:08:41,779
Yes!

90
00:08:51,879 --> 00:08:53,000
Will you trust me?

91
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:56,000
Depends on who's asking.

92
00:08:57,559 --> 00:08:59,000
I know you won't reveal yourself,

93
00:08:59,559 --> 00:09:01,720
but I don't want
innocents dragged into this.

94
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:06,399
If you're Zhaoxi or the scholar
coming to find his relatives,

95
00:09:07,039 --> 00:09:08,519
I'd never give it to you.

96
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:11,120
But I've investigated General Shen.

97
00:09:11,679 --> 00:09:13,399
He's loyal.

98
00:09:14,039 --> 00:09:17,000
He's the only one I trust
in court to solve this.

99
00:09:17,679 --> 00:09:19,840
If you come as his advisor,

100
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:23,039
then I must ask if I can trust you.

101
00:09:25,639 --> 00:09:27,879
For you, I'd die a thousand deaths.

102
00:09:36,256 --> 00:09:38,245
(Heaven)

103
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:45,480
The Pavilion's Heaven tasks
are highly secret.

104
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:50,080
(But they can't appear
by magic in the Shadow Pavilion.)

105
00:09:51,080 --> 00:09:53,399
(I searched everywhere in the room.
No hidden doors.)

106
00:09:54,039 --> 00:09:57,559
(From the outside, no one ever entered
or opened the secret compartment.)

107
00:09:58,639 --> 00:10:00,519
Since nothing can be taken from outside,

108
00:10:01,519 --> 00:10:04,480
that means the mechanism
must be beneath the secret compartment.

109
00:10:05,519 --> 00:10:07,679
If it is through underground passages,

110
00:10:08,159 --> 00:10:09,600
everything will make sense.

111
00:10:10,559 --> 00:10:12,720
Tunneling this entire underground web

112
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:14,519
without being detected.

113
00:10:14,679 --> 00:10:17,759
You can start investigating
from the capital's drainage pipes.

114
00:10:30,679 --> 00:10:31,559
Go...

115
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:45,000
and hurry back.

116
00:10:54,336 --> 00:10:56,526
♪Carving a monument of longing♪

117
00:10:56,966 --> 00:10:58,790
♪For someone♪

118
00:10:59,008 --> 00:11:03,398
♪I know the past can never be relived♪

119
00:11:04,358 --> 00:11:06,694
♪Life after life♪

120
00:11:07,296 --> 00:11:09,542
(Fufeng Pavilion)

121
00:11:10,425 --> 00:11:14,080
♪I've failed you♪

122
00:11:15,680 --> 00:11:17,542
♪Pour this worldly brew♪

123
00:11:18,368 --> 00:11:20,198
♪I raise my cup♪

124
00:11:20,198 --> 00:11:24,634
♪Accompany you through ups and downs♪

125
00:11:25,760 --> 00:11:27,904
♪Tears of romance♪

126
00:11:28,294 --> 00:11:31,475
♪You smile so sadly♪

127
00:11:31,700 --> 00:11:35,488
♪It tears me apart inside♪

128
00:11:36,576 --> 00:11:39,214
♪Ask the demons♪

129
00:11:39,214 --> 00:11:41,518
♪Born with guilt♪

130
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:44,105
♪Laugh at the gods♪

131
00:11:44,105 --> 00:11:45,975
♪I have no regrets♪

132
00:11:46,880 --> 00:11:49,121
♪This sorrow♪

133
00:11:49,536 --> 00:11:52,025
♪Endless tears♪

134
00:11:52,416 --> 00:11:54,892
♪Drunk for you♪

135
00:12:05,759 --> 00:12:06,720
Why ask me to meet here?

136
00:12:07,159 --> 00:12:08,159
Too many eyes.

137
00:12:10,799 --> 00:12:13,000
Any news about those people
I asked you to find?

138
00:12:14,360 --> 00:12:15,200
I found them.

139
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:18,080
Those beggars stole from a household.

140
00:12:18,279 --> 00:12:21,240
When I arrived, they were
beaten half to death.

141
00:12:22,279 --> 00:12:24,000
I've ordered them to be well cared for.

142
00:12:25,039 --> 00:12:27,720
But why seek out beggars?

143
00:12:30,879 --> 00:12:33,840
You travel widely for trade,
and your connections are vast.

144
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:37,039
Even the Xuanji Pavilion
couldn't find them, but you did.

145
00:12:41,279 --> 00:12:43,240
You asked me out just for this?

146
00:12:45,159 --> 00:12:46,120
Of course not.

147
00:12:47,440 --> 00:12:49,360
Ensure those are well protected.

148
00:12:50,360 --> 00:12:52,799
I've cleared your name
regarding the Yunya Temple incident

149
00:12:53,639 --> 00:12:56,720
and handed the one who stole your pouch
at the banquet to the officials.

150
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:59,679
You could have let your servant tell me.

151
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:01,279
Why ask me to meet here?

152
00:13:02,960 --> 00:13:04,480
Xuan Qing isn't a servant.

153
00:13:06,759 --> 00:13:09,120
Fine, whatever you say.

154
00:13:10,879 --> 00:13:14,919
But what's your real purpose
of asking me out today?

155
00:13:15,399 --> 00:13:18,679
There's a circus performing today.
The new year is approaching.

156
00:13:19,480 --> 00:13:22,720
The streets are getting lively.

157
00:13:23,960 --> 00:13:26,639
I hear there's going to be
a molten iron fireworks show later.

158
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:28,600
Would you like to watch with me?

159
00:13:30,720 --> 00:13:32,480
That's the thing Wenshuang enjoys.

160
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:37,799
You invited me to watch fireworks?

161
00:13:39,919 --> 00:13:43,080
Where's Zhaoxi?
I haven't seen him lately.

162
00:13:43,559 --> 00:13:45,000
The iron fireworks show will begin.

163
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:46,080
- Let's go!
- Alright.

164
00:13:46,080 --> 00:13:47,039
Let's grab a good spot.

165
00:13:48,080 --> 00:13:49,159
Molten iron fireworks.

166
00:13:56,080 --> 00:13:59,600
Master Chaosheng, it's too crowded.
We should head back.

167
00:14:19,392 --> 00:14:24,455
♪Willows sway in the twilight breeze♪

168
00:14:26,239 --> 00:14:31,820
♪Old dreams flow like melodious poetry♪

169
00:14:32,909 --> 00:14:36,184
♪Memories fade like the passing years♪

170
00:14:36,184 --> 00:14:39,360
♪The past events leave us confused♪

171
00:14:42,360 --> 00:14:45,559
Strolling with another man
before our wedding?

172
00:14:45,919 --> 00:14:49,639
Did you assume I wouldn't return
and start seeking replacement?

173
00:14:52,519 --> 00:14:54,519
How was I to know if you'd return?

174
00:14:55,159 --> 00:14:56,600
Of course I made alternative plans.

175
00:14:58,840 --> 00:15:01,120
With you here, I'll always return.

176
00:15:03,399 --> 00:15:05,879
If I journey far again,
I'll tell you my return date.

177
00:15:06,432 --> 00:15:13,472
♪Zither strings sigh
for the sorrow parting♪

178
00:15:13,472 --> 00:15:20,244
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

179
00:15:20,244 --> 00:15:27,380
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

180
00:15:27,380 --> 00:15:31,764
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

181
00:15:31,764 --> 00:15:34,176
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

182
00:15:34,176 --> 00:15:41,022
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

183
00:15:41,022 --> 00:15:47,572
♪With nothing but memories left♪

184
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:02,799
He's watching.

185
00:16:10,120 --> 00:16:11,080
How do you know?

186
00:16:11,639 --> 00:16:14,799
You invited Gu Chaosheng out
just for him to see this, didn't you?

187
00:16:19,120 --> 00:16:21,519
Last time, we missed
the molten iron fireworks.

188
00:16:21,639 --> 00:16:23,759
This time, it's perfect.

189
00:16:33,919 --> 00:16:35,000
May I kiss you?

190
00:16:36,120 --> 00:16:36,759
My dear?

191
00:16:57,984 --> 00:17:01,120
- Great.
- Great.

192
00:17:01,677 --> 00:17:07,128
♪I want to hold tight
this love on the wind♪

193
00:17:08,646 --> 00:17:14,118
♪Even if it's just fleeting joy♪

194
00:17:14,560 --> 00:17:20,582
♪It can become a memory I'll hold onto♪

195
00:17:21,792 --> 00:17:26,417
♪If halfway through, you leave me♪

196
00:17:28,079 --> 00:17:33,291
♪I'd still welcome another storm♪

197
00:17:35,031 --> 00:17:40,286
♪Our stolen moment passes too soon♪

198
00:17:40,822 --> 00:17:47,435
♪Unable to wait for this love to bloom♪

199
00:17:49,126 --> 00:17:51,366
♪Who isn't just a passerby♪

200
00:17:51,366 --> 00:17:54,086
♪And whose only one are you♪

201
00:17:54,368 --> 00:17:55,718
♪Who broke♪

202
00:17:56,032 --> 00:17:57,462
♪Whose heart♪

203
00:17:58,000 --> 00:17:58,920
He's still here?

204
00:18:01,960 --> 00:18:02,559
Yes.

205
00:18:04,422 --> 00:18:07,206
♪Letting tears run wild♪

206
00:18:07,552 --> 00:18:09,926
♪Only then realizing your hand♪

207
00:18:09,926 --> 00:18:13,954
♪Holds my thread♪

208
00:18:28,440 --> 00:18:30,200
Was your trip successful?

209
00:18:32,359 --> 00:18:34,559
I've delivered the item to General Shen.

210
00:18:34,799 --> 00:18:37,279
Good news should arrive within days.

211
00:18:39,039 --> 00:18:41,200
Do you have any suspicions
about the mastermind?

212
00:18:41,400 --> 00:18:43,920
No rush. You may close the trap first.

213
00:18:44,240 --> 00:18:49,200
After all, the one the scroll leads to
likely isn't the true hand.

214
00:18:55,039 --> 00:18:57,519
How have you been during my absence?

215
00:18:57,920 --> 00:19:00,680
Why do I return to see this spectacle?

216
00:19:03,160 --> 00:19:05,039
Haven't you already guessed this?

217
00:19:05,759 --> 00:19:08,640
As for the show, that depends
entirely on your performance.

218
00:19:11,160 --> 00:19:15,240
Our wedding approaches.
Protect yourself well.

219
00:19:16,799 --> 00:19:20,720
This frail body still
relies on your protection.

220
00:19:22,880 --> 00:19:26,279
Why this sudden urgency
to smoke them out?

221
00:19:26,880 --> 00:19:28,119
If my deduction holds,

222
00:19:28,680 --> 00:19:32,799
it's all the family head's design.

223
00:19:42,920 --> 00:19:43,559
Master.

224
00:19:43,599 --> 00:19:46,400
Where have you been at this hour?

225
00:20:21,918 --> 00:20:26,981
♪Willows sway in the twilight breeze♪

226
00:20:27,518 --> 00:20:32,839
♪Ancient alleys guard time's secrets♪

227
00:20:33,406 --> 00:20:40,034
♪Bluestones bear life's imprints♪

228
00:20:40,034 --> 00:20:44,798
♪Falling petals, endless longing♪

229
00:20:44,798 --> 00:20:47,134
♪Longing lingers within my heart♪

230
00:20:47,134 --> 00:20:53,834
♪Zither strings sigh
for the sorrow parting♪

231
00:20:53,834 --> 00:21:00,606
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

232
00:21:00,606 --> 00:21:07,742
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

233
00:21:07,742 --> 00:21:12,126
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

234
00:21:12,126 --> 00:21:14,750
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

235
00:21:14,750 --> 00:21:21,384
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

236
00:21:21,384 --> 00:21:27,934
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

237
00:21:27,934 --> 00:21:35,058
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

238
00:21:35,148 --> 00:21:39,518
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

239
00:21:39,518 --> 00:21:42,226
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

240
00:21:42,226 --> 00:21:48,126
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

241
00:21:48,766 --> 00:21:54,754
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪
